  create view "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_no_mb_clients__dbt_tmp" include schema privileges as (
    with base as
(
select 		    Master_Account_ID 
                , Master_Account_Name 
                , bundle_type 
                , round(sum(units),0) as units
                , round(sum(charge),0) as charge
                , round(sum(Revenue_USD),0) as Revenue_USD

group by 	    1,2,3
order by 	    Master_Account_ID 
)
, pmix as
(
select 		    *
			    , count(Master_Account_ID) over (partition by Master_Account_ID ) as cnt
from 		    base
)
select 		    *
from 		    pmix
where 		    cnt = 1 
                and bundle_type = 'package'
  );, Message: CommandComplete: command_tag = "CREATE VIEW", Code: None, Rows: -1, Arraysize: 1

Operation: /* {"app": "dbt", "dbt_version": "1.4.4", "profile_name": "GM", "target_name": "dev", "node_id": "model.GM.oy_dbt_revenue_sms_KSA"} */

  
    create  table
    "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_revenue_sms_KSA__dbt_tmp"
    
    INCLUDE SCHEMA PRIVILEGES as (
    

with base as 
(
select 		    c.*
                , case when b.Master_Account_ID is not null then '1' else 0 end as no_mb_client
                , case when i.Master_Account_ID is not null then '1' else 0 end as sell_rate_invalid
from            "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_consumption_agg_sms_KSA" as c
----------------
left join       (select distinct Master_Account_ID from "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_no_mb_clients") as b 
on              c.Master_Account_ID = b.Master_Account_ID
----------------
left join       (select distinct Master_Account_ID from "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_clients_with_invalid_selling_rate") as i 
on              c.Master_Account_ID = i.Master_Account_ID
where           1=1
                and c.date_nk >= '2023-08-01' 
                --and c.date_nk <= '2023-10-10' -- this filter is because from '2023-10-12' Alinma bank started to consume mb. I'll remove this filter later.
				--and c.cost_id is not null -- to exclude failovers
)
select          * 
from            base
where           1=1
                --and no_mb_client = 1
                and sell_rate_invalid = 0
  )
 

  

    
 
  ;

  
      
        
    

      , Message: CommandComplete: command_tag = "CREATE TABLE", Code: None, Rows: -1, Arraysize: 1

Operation: /* {"app": "dbt", "dbt_version": "1.4.4", "profile_name": "GM", "target_name": "dev", "node_id": "model.GM.oy_dbt_gross_margin_KSA"} */

  
    create  table
    "verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_gross_margin_KSA__dbt_tmp"
    
    INCLUDE SCHEMA PRIVILEGES as (
    

select 			c.rep_month 
				, c.date_nk 
				, c.charging_id 
				, c.Master_Account_ID 
				, c.Master_Account_Name 
				, c.cost_id 
				, c.consumption 
				, c.charge
				, c.chargeable_units
				, t.units as traffic
				, c.Revenue_USD 
				, t.COGS_USD
				, case when t.COGS_USD is null then c.Revenue_USD
					   else c.Revenue_USD - t.COGS_USD 
					   end as Gross_Profit_USD
				, c.GP_USD_estimate
				, case when t.COGS_USD is null or t.COGS_USD = 0 then null 
					   else round(100*(c.Revenue_USD/t.COGS_USD - 1), 2) 
					   end as Gross_Margin_pct
				, case when c.Revenue_USD is null or c.Revenue_USD = 0 then null
					   else round(100*(c.GP_USD_estimate/c.Revenue_USD), 2) 
					   end as GM_pct_estimate
				, t.cost_rate_USD 
				, t.cost_rate
				, t.currency
				, t.network_name
				, t.operator_name
				, c.categorized_charge_pct
				, c.charge_with_cost_id_pct
from 			"verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_revenue_sms_KSA_agg" as c
left join 		"verticadb"."analytics"."oy_dbt_KSA_COGS_excl_failover_agg" as t
on				c.date_nk = t.date_nk 
				and c.cost_id = t.cost_id 
				and c.charging_id = t.charging_id 
where 			1=1
--order by 		charging_id , cost_id
  )
 

  

    
 
  ;

  
      
        
    

      , Message: CommandComplete: command_tag = "CREATE TABLE", Code: None, Rows: -1, Arraysize: 1
